<i>adverb</i>: 열심히 [열씸히], 극구 [극꾸] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>열심히 [열씸히]</dt><br>
<dd>hard; diligently; zealously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 온 정성을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>With all one's heart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>극구 [극꾸]</dt><br>
<dd>aggressively; zealously</dd><br>
<dd>온갖 말이나 행동을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>With every sort of words or actions.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>